Paper: hep-th/9411145

Date: 1994-11-18

Title: Quantum Affine Algebras and their Representations

Authors: V. Chari and A.N.Pressley

Comments: 19 pages

We prove a highest weight theorem classifying irerducible finite--dimensionalrepresentations of quantum affine algebras and survey what is currently knownabout the structure of these representations.